subtitle.text: What's wrong, little hippies? Your great gnu leader is missing?
Oh yes, see, he's in my castle now and will be served for supper...
But I'm a fair creature, so I'll make you a deal.
If you can beat me at racing, I will free the old codger.
But you pathetic little twerps will never be able to beat me - King of the Karts!
